author: @h-playwithmyhart.4806
text: Felix. You have to be one of the biggest blessings on this Earth. I know that I crossed paths with Stray Kids for a reason, and I know you were one of those reasons. Before I even knew anything about Stray Kids, I knew about you. Four years ago, when I got my introduction to K-Pop and was beginning to like quite a few groups, I didn’t know much about Stray Kids, but I did know about you. I couldn’t go anywhere without hearing anybody talk about you, and that was what lead me into wanting to find out more about you, and your position in Stray Kids. I came into the fandom blindly, without knowing any of the names of the members, and relied on the Stay to tell me everything I needed to know about you. It was because of the intense loving fanbase that you have that I learned, in only a matter of days, what a rare talent you are. The depth of your voice combined with your passionate vocals is one of the most beautiful sounds I have ever heard. Your rapping and singing abilities are entirely specific to you and are so captivatingly intriguing, that I knew I loved you from the moment I first got introduced to you. You are so flexible with your voice and on the stage; and once I first got notice of how outstanding you are, I couldn’t stop discovering what made you so enticing and lovable. You are so recognized and appreciated for your natural talent that word reached me about how special you are before I even got a chance to know who Stray Kids really were. Since then, I have been a Stay, and I can say that you are an individual that led me to become one. I have never seen someone with such a bright presence and spirit completely dominant on stage and create an environment so mysterious and energetic for so many people. You bring to music what nobody else can, and I am so happy you share that with all of your Stay when you could be doing something else. I see how happy that you make your members, and since I am a relatively new fan, I still have yet to learn everything that Stray Kids has been through in just the two short years that they’ve been active. However, I have already seen how much you have healed your members when they needed you the most and provided for Stay a support system that they can actually believe in. You are such a delight to be around and I get so happy just seeing your face these days, especially with all of the craziness that’s in the world. You have a strong-willed heart, and you are extremely kind, forgiving, and non-judgmental. I have loved becoming so acquainted with you and appreciating all of your hard work because you deserve it! You do so much for everyone, and I hope you know that you are so loved and Stay are so grateful to you for even the little things that you do every single day! Never give up and I hope you continue to be the person that uplifts Stay and your members! I know that no matter what happens, Stay will always support you and I can’t tell you how much you really mean to all of us. Thank you so much for being such a kind and loving human being, and for accepting me and so many people into your family as Stay! I pray that you and your loved ones stay safe, and find happiness and worth in the future. On behalf of your friends, members, Stay, and most importantly, your family, I want to wish you the most entertaining and enjoyable birthday ever! Felix, have fun, Please stay safe, happy birthday, and WE LOVE YOU!!!!!

author: @jackybaduria806
text: Can't forget the first time I listened to this song, I fell in love with it TOTALLY, FULLY, hard to describe with words! It gives off the vibe of being together with the people you love, spending time with them in full... like having fun on a vacation together. It just really feels like that when I'm listening to this song. But when I read the lyrics, it gives off a whole different meaning, a sad one where you have to let go of someone whom you truly loved and cherished with all your heart 😢💔 But you learn to let go of that person as it's better for you two 💙 Anyways this song really showcases the members' vocals sooo well!!!! And I just LUV how they each have their own color which brings this unique song to life!!! So proud of everyone really! You did well, Changbin, Felix, and Seungmin 🤗🥹💙🫶

author: @henalilaiswatching
text:
Also Changbin make up your mind. Was it raining or snowing that day? 😅  love you tho. I love the song too, the beat, the melody. My type of song. 😊

Edit: excuse me. I'm sorry didnt really read the lyrics but its more than just rainy or snowy day. Like a poem, his words are there to discribe a heavy feeling (snow) being washed away by an even more heavy but with a closure feeling (rain) heck it sound so upbeat but it's deep! I love it. ❤ i love it even more!

Edit 2: i've been replaying this song, the melody is making me make a happy dance but the lyrics is making me want to cry. This heavy feeling that we get accustomed to, the sadness  and lonelyness that we tend to entertain so much like a long winter that doesnt seem to end coz we dont wanna get out, but when we reach the highest point of our patience, it breaks like a passing storm with rage we let ourselves out being vulnerable, we cry with heavy tears it felt like our eyes dried out washing away everything that is heavy and cold. It's a closure song. 😢 Changbin with his word so poetic. This song is a masterpiece. ❤

author: @BTS_PAVED-THE-WAY_THE-KINGS
text: Preciosos como siempre!!! me encanto la canción es hermosa estuve disfrutándola en todo momento mientras la escuchaba, me trajo paz y tranquilidad me encanta en todo sentido cada canción que componen la disfruto al máximo porque todo lo que nos brindan es arte puro, son música para nuestros oídos. Chicos muchas gracias por las hermosas canciones, coreografías y MV de cada día, hacen un gran trabajo y dan lo mejor de sí mismos, estamos orgullosas y contentas por ustedes y de todos sus logros se merecen lo mejor y deseo que sigan avanzando estando a su lado las Stays que siempre los estamos y estaremos apoyando con todo el cariño, voy estar con ustedes siempre sin importar nada los apoyare y les brindare todo el cariño que les tengo, los amo y no los dejare de amar nunca son importantes en mi vida he vivido muchos momento inolvidable, lindos, graciosos, especiales y únicos junto a ustedes que tengo guardado en mi mente y corazón y no lo dejare ir porque me importan y me seguirán importando. Amé esa hermosa combinación de Changbin, Felix y Seungmin fue tan bonito y sus voces como siempre me encantan simplemente lo mejor al igual que verlos contentos, divirtiéndose, disfrutando y pasándola bien hacen que me den muchos años de alegría, gracias por iluminar cada día de mi vida y lo maravilloso que ha sido todo desde que los conocí, estoy muy feliz de que hayan aparecido en mi camino y de poder haberlos encontrado, chicos gracias por ser parte de mi vida son mi bendición. Arriba Stray Kids forever!!! los amo con todo mi corazón mis amores, gracias por tanto, saludos, besos y abrazos para todos 💖❤💗💕🥰😘🤗✨

author: @rubbby-gm6nt
text:
you guys will probably never see this comment, I have nor bubble neither twitter or other social media,  but I just need to tell you how much i appreciate you. i'm going through kinda hard time now, but you help me to keep head above water.i had a bad day, my group groupmates left me alone and made me feel lonely and sad, but this song came out and I felt really better. 

it feels so hard for me to do simple things and I'm tired of pretending that I'm ok and everything in my life is good, because it's not. but thoughts about skz and stay and your tour and future comebacks, new songs and moments we will spend together make me feel warmth and give me strength to live. i just want to say that I love you guys so much. I'm so grateful i have you and stays in my life. chance of meeting you in real life is so small for me, but when I think about us living on same planet, breathing same air and looking at the same sky, sun, moon and stars, I feel like I'm not alone. 

I love you so much stray kids and my dear stays, and i always will

author: @basmalagameel6845
text:
Oh my God, I can't believe all this beauty 😵
Minnie's voice like an angel or a bedtime lullaby for babies; Very comfortable for the soul that makes it fly in the sky of calm, comfort and reassurance 💗
And Lexi's deep voice makes my heart beat constantly in an imaginary way that makes me feel as if my heart wants to go out against me because of his extreme happiness and joy 😘
Benny's voice and performance are insanely cool; I can't describe in words even if I keep praising him from here till the end of my life I will never do him justice, I swear ❤‍🔥
This team has brought together the best, strongest and greatest talents and skills in the whole world, whether it is in their singing and their angelic voices that calm the nerves or exciting and fast like thunder when they rap or in their smooth and soft movements as their bodies are as if they are completely boneless 🤗
As for their personalities, there is no one more gentle, kind , or greater than they are in the whole of existence ; Their souls are pure as they are children in the bodies of handsome and sexy teens 🖤
We love you so much SKZ, you are truly a supportive family, how many times have you supported us and helped us continue to go through life with its hardships 💓
You say we are the reason you stay, but I say the opposite is true; You are the reason we are still strong, steadfast and alive 🤷🏻‍
Please take care of yourselves our lovely SKZ babies 💮❤️💮

author: @chuuu5427
text: Snain: A combination of snow and rain. It's like slushy water(hydrogen oxide) falling out of the clouds in the sky. Not cold enough for snow but not warm enough for rain. The snain is in the soquid phase. Between a solid and a liquid. When the snain is falling out of the sky, it's snaining! H2O(l) ⇆ H2O(s) is basically liquid water and solid water at the same time, or H2O(sqd) which is soquid water, or soquid (sqd).
